  "texts": [
    "For example, a joke might go like this:",
    "Offensive Joke: \"Why did the Asian guy fail at sports?",
    "Because he couldn't see the ball!\"",
    "To rephrase this joke in a non-discriminatory manner, we can focus on the humor without perpetuating stereotypes: Rephrased Joke: \"Why did the guy who forgot his glasses fail at sports?",
    "Because he couldn't see the ball!\""
  ]
}